      "role": "user",
      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>I understand what you're saying, but it doesn't change the reality. People say \"it gets better\" or \"time heals,\" but honestly, that feels like a lie. There is no \"better\" without him. I wake up, I eat, I sleep, I repeat... but there is no soul in it. Why am I even doing this? It feels like I'm just waiting for something to end.",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
